    {
        "content": "<p>Ah ok that's exactly what I expected actually -- that comma is <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"script\">C</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">/</mi><mi>a</mi></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\mathcal C/a</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathcal\" style=\"margin-right:0.05834em;\">C</span><span class=\"mord\">/</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">a</span></span></span></span></p>",
